These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, may, march
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the person who's birthday is in october##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Birthday      | may  | october | march        | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, game, ritmeester, pall-mall
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the ritmeester-smoker##7
2. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
3. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the game-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Cigar     | ritmeester | game       | pall-mall         | bolivar     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, skydiving, board-games, traveling
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is camping##7
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Hobby   | board-games | camping  | traveling   | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
City: miami, berlin, edinburgh, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person traveling to berlin and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| City   | berlin      | miami   | edinburgh | boston  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog, rat, frog
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the german is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the rabbit##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet         | rat | rabbit   | frog | hedgehog |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, grey, yellow, brown
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, indonesian, nigerian
1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the indonesian is the person who likes brown##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the person who likes white##1
4. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
5. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
6. the nigerian is somewhere between the american and the dutch##7
7. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the person who likes yellow##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color      | grey | white      | yellow | brown     |
| Nationality   | american    | nigerian | dutch   | indonesian |

