.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, writing, baking, rock-climbing
1. the argentine is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
3. the spanish is the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Hobby           | baking   | rock-climbing    | puzzles       | writing  |

