.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, badminton, handball, biathlon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, pop, r&b, techno
1. the person who's sport is soccer is not the fan of classical##6
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the fan of techno##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person who's sport is badminton##7
6. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Sport           | biathlon | soccer | handball | badminton |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | r&b      | classical | pop            |

