.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, satire, thriller, western
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, baking, collecting, hiking
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
2. the person watching satire movies is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
3. the person who's hobby is baking is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
5. the person watching family movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Hobby           | camping    | baking   | hiking  | collecting      |

