2. the dressmaker is on the left of the journalist##1
3. the designer is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the designer##2
6. the dressmaker is somewhere between the designer and the person watching documentary movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | animation | documentary | epic   |
| Job   | designer    | dressmaker      | journalist      | paramedic |

