2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the fan of folk is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
5. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
