.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
City: san-francisco, berlin, boston, nizza
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, subway, trike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the subway is the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to boston is not the person driving the bus##6
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person traveling to boston##7
7. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| City       | nizza | san-francisco | berlin | boston |
| Transport   | bike   | trike      | bus        | subway  |

