.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-15::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, tomato, kiwi
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, paramedic
1. the person eating kiwi is somewhere between the person eating avocado and the paramedic##7
2. the architect is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
3. the paramedic is on the far left##1
4. the person eating avocado is not the paramedic##6
5. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the architect and the freelancer##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Food   | tomato | kiwi     | artichoke     | avocado |
| Job     | paramedic | freelancer | firefighter | architect     |

