2. the coach is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the mechanic is on the right of the architect##1
4. the engineer is somewhere between the coach and the cottage house##7
5. the colonial house is somewhere between the craftsman house and the architect##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Job           | architect | mechanic | engineer | coach  |
| House   | cottage     | colonial   | craftsman    | cape-cod |

