.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, soy-milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: kale, garlic, blueberry, zucchini
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking fanta##7
2. the person drinking tea is between the person eating blueberry and the person eating zucchini##2
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
6. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage    | fanta   | lemonade  | tea  | soy-milk |
| Food   | garlic | blueberry | kale | zucchini    |

