2. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes blue is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
6. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
