.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish, snake
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, pomegranate, cauliflower, asparagus
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | ferret    | goldfish | snake     | dog |
| Food   | cauliflower | asparagus  | pomegranate | eggplant |

 